                '<p>Your Professional provides end-to-end support for increasing authorized capital \u2014 from initial assessment of your capital requirements and calculating state-specific stamp duty to drafting board and shareholder resolutions, preparing EGM notices, filing Form SH-7 with the ROC, amending the MOA, and ensuring complete MCA compliance. Our experienced CS professionals ensure a smooth, error-free process completed within the statutory timelines.</p>',
